Information about articles, essays, reviews, and interviews was added. IDed a few names in the text.

/* God's Shadow */ Since this is an entry on Alan Mikhail as a whole, we added information about his entire career, not just the latest book. We describe each of his books and discuss both positive and negative reviews to provide balance. We edited the portion on God's Shadow to give balance there too. This meant adding examples from multiple reviews. Some general edited was done too to remove spelling and other mistakes.
